N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 5 ยง 120.9 - Reporting

State Regulations

Every eligible applicant participating in the service shall
provide the department with such reports relating to such participation as the
commissioner shall deem to be necessary or desirable. Notes
